{"tid":1720524,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【殺戮戰場好心痛】生日不快樂 黃家強：說聲天佑香港","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:52:51.000Z","uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db270886dfa4609036f052dc838d909a7e3fd22f","tid":1720524,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20191113/s00009/c7652e63fe2b72c5691f7a2af93c1265.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20191113%2Fs00009%2Fc7652e63fe2b72c5691f7a2af93c1265.jpg&h=92ebdd8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃家強55歲生日（11月13日），家強於凌晨上載黑白的蛋糕照片，留言：「一個非常之不快樂的生日，不要和我說生日快樂，大家為香港祈禱，說聲『天佑香港』吧!」家強一直低調關心社會情況，於7月底他在facebook分享歌曲《殺戮戰場》MV，留言：「心痛！天佑香港！」。《殺戮戰場》是家強作曲，作詞兼主唱，其中歌詞：「這殺戮 誰去擴張 亡命方向 你殺我 我殺你 殺到慌張 冤冤相報的 未必可釋放 都使你心中有罪 難以制止 忘掉方向 殺戮戰場都使你心中有罪 難以制止 忘掉方向 殺戮戰場.. ... 」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191113/1573581266575/【殺戮戰場好心痛】生日不快樂-黃家強-說聲天佑香港\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191113%2F1573581266575%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AE%BA%E6%88%AE%E6%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E5%A5%BD%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B%E3%80%91%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%B6%E5%BC%B7-%E8%AA%AA%E8%81%B2%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVcwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=d295dcca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191113%2F1573581266575%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AE%BA%E6%88%AE%E6%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E5%A5%BD%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B%E3%80%91%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82-%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%B6%E5%BC%B7-%E8%AA%AA%E8%81%B2%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF&h=9ff667e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191113/1573581266575/【殺戮戰場好心痛】生日不快樂-黃家強-說聲天佑香港</a>"},{"pid":"fabf30d471a97763cee0252c7ac8031b98c72c88","tid":1720524,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit